The "Find*.cmake" files in this directory are modelled closely after
those found in the HPX library at
<https://github.com/STEllAR-GROUP/hpx>. We gratefully acknowledge the
HPX developers' contribution to the open source landscape.

The "Coveralls*.cmake" files in this directory are taken from
<https://github.com/JoakimSoderberg/coveralls-cmake>.
